title: IT IS NO LONGER I THAT LIVETH
bible_ref: I am crucified with Christ: nevertheless I live; yet not I, but Christ liveth in me: Gal. 2:20
verses: It is no longer I that liveth,=But Christ that liveth in me=It is no longer I that liveth,=But Christ that liveth in me,=He lives in me,=Jesus is the life in me=It is no longer I that liveth,=But Christ that liveth in me
